  {'date': '2026-04-21', 'title': 'Provision in the Wilderness', 'scripture': 'Exodus 16:15', 'body': 'When the Israelites saw it, they said to each other, "What is it?" For they did not know what it was. Moses said to them, "It is the bread the LORD has given you to eat."', 'story': 'Rita felt lost in a wilderness season. She didn\'t know where to turn. Then God provided—not in the way she expected, but in provision perfectly suited to her need. She realized: in wilderness seasons, God doesn\'t lead you out; He feeds you through.', 'thoughts': 'God provides in wilderness seasons. Trust His provision.', 'action': 'Look for today\'s provision. Thank God for it.', 'confession': 'Thank You for providing in my wilderness. I trust You. Amen.', 'author': 'NLCC'},
  
  {'date': '2026-04-22', 'title': 'The Power of Words', 'scripture': 'Proverbs 18:21', 'body': 'The tongue has the power of life and death, and those who love it will eat its fruit.', 'story': 'Samuel realized his words had tremendous power. Careless comments had wounded people deeply. Encouraging words had lifted others up. He began speaking intentionally—using his words to give life. His words became seeds that bore fruit in people\'s lives.', 'thoughts': 'Your words have power. Speak life.', 'action': 'Speak life to someone today. Choose your words carefully.', 'confession': 'Help me to speak life, not death. Guard my tongue. Amen.', 'author': 'NLCC'},
  
  {'date': '2026-04-23', 'title': 'The Faithfulness of God Through Generations', 'scripture': 'Deuteronomy 7:9', 'body': 'Know therefore that the LORD your God is God; he is the faithful God, keeping his covenant of love to a thousand generations.', 'story': 'Tanya discovered her grandmother\'s journals. She saw how God had been faithful across three generations—protecting, guiding, providing. She realized her relationship with God wasn\'t beginning with her; it was part of a lineage of God\'s faithfulness. That perspective gave her courage.', 'thoughts': 'God\'s faithfulness extends across generations. You are part of His story.', 'action': 'Thank God for His faithfulness to your family line.', 'confession': 'Thank You for being faithful to my family across generations. Amen.', 'author': 'NLCC'},
  
  {'date': '2026-04-24', 'title': 'The Community of Faith', 'scripture': 'Hebrews 10:24-25', 'body': 'And let us consider how we may spur one another on toward love and good deeds, not giving up meeting together, as some are in the habit of doing, but encouraging one another.', 'story': 'Uma went through a season of spiritual isolation. She didn\'t attend church, didn\'t connect with believers. Her faith dried up. When she returned to community, something shifted. The encouragement, accountability, and love of God\'s people revived her faith. Community wasn\'t optional; it was essential.', 'thoughts': 'Community is essential to faith. Don\'t isolate.', 'action': 'Connect with believers today. Let them encourage you.', 'confession': 'Help me to be committed to community and to spur others on. Amen.', 'author': 'NLCC'},
  
